\begin_inset Formula $\muB_{\rho}$
\end_inset

 defined as 
\begin_inset Formula $\muB_{\rho}\left(P\right)=\Tr\left(\rho P\right)=\sum_{j=1}^{N}q_{j}\muB_{\Phi_{j}}\left(P\right)$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
